title: Man United's Transfer Dartboard
description:
The FC crew look back at the first two matchdays of the Premier League season and break down if any of their preseason predictions have changed drastically. Plus, the guys analyze Manchester United's transfer targets, question as to why Casemiro would even want to go to the club and Julien Laurens joins the show to analyze the penalty drama brewing in Paris.
